{"tid":1563263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"多圖／TWICE志效男友來台啦　姜丹尼爾揮手電翻粉絲","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:44:12.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0702a9d131b624ba9f623201b730b51ea7a50905","tid":1563263,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1568266170-8bb44ac82d5a619f493bc57396457ed3-696x464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1568266170-8bb44ac82d5a619f493bc57396457ed3-696x464.jpg&h=5806045c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓團Wanna One人氣成員姜丹尼爾今年自團體解散後，發行專輯展開個人活動，並舉辦「Color on me」亞洲巡迴見面會，台灣站將於明晚在南港展覽館登場，他今（12日）提早抵台做準備，儘管是上班上課時間，仍有破百名粉絲接機，人氣不容小覷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1568266152-c215892d7404304d0a99369669db0875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1568266152-c215892d7404304d0a99369669db0875.jpg&h=2f81c917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲姜丹尼爾來台。（圖／記者林柏年攝）<br />\n<br />\n姜丹尼爾8月初認愛TWICE隊長志效，但他人氣不減，今中午抵台時，儘管班機延遲20分鐘，仍有百位粉絲接機；他身穿白色帽T，把背包掛在胸前，一現身就讓出境大廳尖叫聲不斷，雖然沒多做停留，但走去座車1分多鐘的路途中，不斷向粉絲揮手致意，相當親民。<br />\n<br />\n他明晚6點半將在南港展覽館4F雲端展場舉辦粉絲見面會，現場可購票。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/1568266193-6e91d2b5a38ec5bed990132cda4f2886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F1568266193-6e91d2b5a38ec5bed990132cda4f2886.jpg&h=700d36b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37a60ef3ae192e3abe979431c3534840e50a7822","tid":1563263,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f1a76b73c32ca1d7a4ce46b7768d2952af430416","tid":1563263,"uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"好襯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣咁柒"},{"pid":"04d2c057a3b513a875e564cdab42b627c8fc228f","tid":1563263,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"姜丹斷腳"},{"pid":"00167972ff223fb845271bea5340194e923e31b1","tid":1563263,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:50:14.000Z","msg":"其實係咪全世界得連登反姜丹<br />\n我見其她地方都撐wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c87537f318c0be9dbb520551fbdc22853442c1","tid":1563263,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1a76b73c32ca1d7a4ce46b7768d2952af430416","tid":1563263,"uid":33359,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"好襯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一樣咁柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:53:19.000Z","msg":"是"},{"pid":"5e1d72cb406cb6ae0bb48498ee82a210e6811b26","tid":1563263,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"斬佢碌鳩落黎，煲湯！"},{"pid":"1c27d69855a174ff16343649f8172d06ed872608","tid":1563263,"uid":167880,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,